er LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Many doctors lack the necessary knowledge and experience to confidently diagnose ME/CFS.</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Due to the historical background</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, some doctors sti</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ll refuse to accept that ME/CFS exists as a clinical entity or are unwilling to use it as a diagnostic label.</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Consequently, a significant proportion of people with ME/CFS remain undiagnosed, misdiagnosed, or have to wait for an unacceptable period of time before the diagnosis is made.</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">2</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">A report by the ME Alliance (R</span><span style="color:#343434; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">7</span><span style="color:#343434; font